        <h3 class="blogTitle">School Closure Extended</h3>
        <div class="blogSubTitle">
            <span class="blogSubTitle-date">Posted on: March 30, 2020</span>
            <br>
</div>
        <div class="blogContentSection">
            
<div class="textholder"> 	
 	
	                <div class="textholder-image" style="float: right; width: 220px; margin-left: 20px;"> 
	                      	                        
	                    <img src="https://www.southwestschools.org/pages/district-news/image/section-image/Closed-302.jpg" alt="Closed" style="width: 212px">
</div>
	<p>Governor DeWine extended the closure of all Ohio schools through at least Friday, May 1.   Click <a href="http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/fdwE68rLQzj2xnvEeGwu5g~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgZQauP0QcaHR0cHM6Ly95b3V0dS5iZS9NQ2hqdnNPV3NHOFcHc2Nob29sbUIKAAAu04Ne2RveB1IgbWlrZS5tb3JyaXNAc291dGh3ZXN0c2Nob29scy5vcmdYBAAAAAE~" target="_blank">HERE</a> for the latest updates from Superintendent John Hamstra.</p>
<p>Thanks to our staff, students and parents for a great start to Remote Learning.  If you are having difficulties, please reach out.  We are here to help and we will get through this together!  </p>
</div>
